{
  "stem": "27509.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They just didn't know how to reconstruct their new life forms and so on, and especially in the ghetto, where there were no opportunities.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the joint provided it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the man-- the man who was managing that enterprise in the ghetto for the-- was a man by the name of Bergman.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a colleague of mine who after the war-- who after the war when he came to America, he gave testimony to the Senate subcommittee about those years.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he visited me here a few years ago.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was here in Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he came to visit in our home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was lecture in-- in-- in the-- just some social sciences, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Japanese.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was policed-- policed is a very mild word.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was policed with a-- with a particular intent.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I would like to come back [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for one particular aspect that I've omitted, but I would like to put it on record.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the days of the kitchen, when I was running the kitchen in Shanghai, before the ghetto was instituted, one day out of the blue, it was after lunch, about 2 o'clock, somebody came into my office and told me that two Japanese people wanted to see you.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I pricked my ears up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's-- sure enough, they came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They started questioning is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What is it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What is the gathering here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We are coming here, well then, what is it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were explained to me the best way I could, that it is a nonprofit organization that provides a hot meal a day for people who are otherwise would have been starving.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so-- yes, but you are Jews here, all Jews here, aren't you?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
